<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping_mim.aggregate_connectivity_requirement_unique_constraint">
The <b>aggregate_connectivity_requirement_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> population members, that fill the role
of ARM <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping:arm:Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping_arm.Aggregate_connectivity_requirement"/>, so that the ARM
<express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping:arm:Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping_arm.Aggregate_connectivity_requirement.design_definition_path"/> attribute shall be unique within the population.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_with_nodal_representation_to_packaged_mapping_mim.aggregate_connectivity_requirement_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> with a name of
'aggregate connectivity requirement' must have a unique
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> attribute that points to a
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> with an id of 'design composition path'.
</ext_description>

